接口 NativeWebSocketSession

  • 所有超级接口:

    public interface NativeWebSocketSession
extends WebSocketSession
    A WebSocketSession that exposes the underlying, native WebSocketSession through a getter.
    从以下版本开始:
    4.0
    作者:
    Rossen Stoyanchev
